# Tech Stack

This project uses the following technologies:

## Backend
- Django (latest LTS version) for web framework
- PostgreSQL for database
- Poetry for dependency management
- Django REST Framework for API endpoints
- Celery for background tasks

## Network Parser Components
- Custom modular parser framework with device-specific implementations
- Support for multiple network device types (Cisco IOS, ASA, Nexus, FortiGate, FortiSwitch, JunOS)

## AI Components
- CrewAI for orchestrating AI-powered workflows
- Langtrace for AI process tracking and debugging
- Integration with OpenAI or similar LLM endpoints

## Frontend
- Django Templates with Bootstrap for basic UI
- JavaScript for enhanced interactions
- Chart.js for data visualization

## Deployment
- Docker and Docker Compose for containerization
- GitHub Actions for CI/CD
- Environment-based configuration

When implementing code for this project, ensure all components follow this stack architecture and leverage the established technologies rather than introducing alternatives without discussion.